// 2. ATTACK SURFACE: List inputs
//    - Login form: username, password fields
//    - Search box: query parameter
//    - URL: /profile?id=123
//    - Cookie: session=abc123
//
// 3. TEST EACH INPUT:
//    - Login form -> SQL injection test
//    - Search box -> XSS test, SQL injection test
//    - URL id param -> IDOR test
//    - Cookie -> session fixation test
//
// 4. CONFIRM: Show the vulnerability working
// 5. IMPACT: What damage could an attacker do?
// 6. DOCUMENT: Evidence for report
